description: Welcome to 232 OC, discover two spacious bedrooms adorned with floor-to-ceiling windows, ushering in an abundance of natural light. The newly designed, modern full bathrooms are a sanctuary of relaxation, boasting spa-like features, with the timeless allure of Carrara marble. Thoughtfully designed, this residence boasts high ceilings, tasteful finishes, and a gourmet kitchen that stands as the heart of the home, featuring a large center island, Jenn Air appliances, custom Italian cabinetry, and premium quartz countertops. This meticulous floor plan maximizes space, providing an abundance of closet space outfitted with full custom shelving. Elevating the experience, a state-of-the-art Sonos sound system sets the stage for an inviting space, perfect for both relaxation and entertaining. Add a deeded garage parking spot with storage space, minutes to the Redline and this becomes one you can not miss!
